name: 李老师不是你老师
content: In an interview with the media on the evening of May 29, Nvidia CEO Huang Renxun said: "Taiwan is one of the most important countries in the world", which sparked heated discussions among netizens. However, as of now, the official media has not publicly criticized Huang Renxun, and related topics have not become hot searches.
